metadata.name: Chubby Cattle #1
metadata.description:
The Chubby Cattle team is proud to present the immersive dining experience of a lifetime.

This industry leading project is the first of its kind to offer free food for life! Each NFT in this collection of 8,888 pieces allows the holder to receive complimentary items at any location that is part of the Chubby Cattle family, along with other member perks including IRL experiences like entry into exclusive events at our venues. Notable locations include The X Pot, Niku X, and Wagyu House in major cities across the United States. The Chubby Cattle digital dining membership project is powered by Moonpay and the w3box platform.
